--- !u!114 &1173562091
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1173562083}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2126b8bce7cfd7742a449b9e7bbbde46, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueManager
  dialogueRoot: {fileID: 306486577}
  dialogueCanvasGroup: {fileID: 0}
  bubbleRect: {fileID: 306486578}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1076965913}
  openFadeDuration: 0.16
  closeFadeDuration: 0.18
  openStartScale: {x: 0.94, y: 0.82, z: 1}
  openOvershootScale: {x: 1.03, y: 1.07, z: 1}
  openSettleDuration: 0.1
  useTalkingJuice: 1
  talkPosAmplitude: 4
  talkPosSpeed: 2.25
  talkScaleXMultiplier: 0.985
  talkScaleYMultiplier: 1.02
  talkScaleSpeed: 2.1
  talkRotationMin: -0.57
  talkRotationMax: 0.54
  talkRotationSpeed: 0.64
  maxVisibleCharactersPerChunk: 37
  dialogueEntries:
  - id: 
    triggerType: 0
    phrase: Hey! You!
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 0
    phrase: Use W A S D to move and E to interact
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.08
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.8
  - id: 
    triggerType: 0
    phrase: 'To start out...

      Make sure to check the PC on your left.'
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.08
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.8
  - id: 
    triggerType: 1
    phrase: This is Giggle!
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 1
    phrase: Go ahead and select the catalog of which you want to get a box of.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 16
    phrase: Pick the boxes and unwrap them using the machine on the top-left corner.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.065
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 7
    phrase: These items can then be packed with the wrapper on your right.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.065
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 7
    phrase: All of them also have special abilities and quirks, so be sure to check
      them first.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.065
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 4
    phrase: When you're done, give that box to your fellow employee at the top.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.06
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 10
    phrase: For each box you sell, you gain money based on item synergies in the
      box.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.06
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 10
    phrase: You can then put that money in the briefcase to fill out the quota in
      time.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 10
    phrase: Simple enough yeah? Now GET TO WORK.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 13
    phrase: The money you put in this briefcase goes to your quota, you have a time
      limit to clear it so be careful... Still, be sure to save some money for boxes.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.07
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.65
  - id: 
    triggerType: 8
    phrase: This is the unwrapper, you need to feed it with boxes from the PC on
      your left.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.06
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.55
  - id: 
    triggerType: 5
    phrase: This is the wrapper, you can pack items here after unwrapping them from
      the boxes.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.06
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 11
    phrase: You need to first get a package ready to deliver using the wrapper on
      your right.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.06
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 14
    phrase: Whenever you spend all your money, you can to take a loan using the button
      on the bottom right. They will ask for interest though, so use this sparingly.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.6
  - id: 
    triggerType: 9
    phrase: Be sure to get some boxes at the PC before coming here.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 6
    phrase: This needs ITEMS, be sure to unwrap them first.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 12
    phrase: Pack your items first before selling them.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 18
    phrase: You've got 1 minute left for the time limit, one slip-up and it's over.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 17
    phrase: Remember to keep up with the quota... Time's ticking.
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  - id: 
    triggerType: 15
    phrase: Remember to take a loan to keep going!
    secondsPerCharacter: 0.05
    holdCompletedTextTime: 0.5
  player: {fileID: 1798789838}
  gameManager: {fileID: 1173562084}
  quotaManager: {fileID: 944592965}
  interactKey: 101
